<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0;">  2.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;"> **</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">기본적으로 Node.js </span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;">24</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;"> 확인</span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;">**</span></span>
